            ]
        }
    ],
    [
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "7. The information sought through the Requested Pen-Trap does not include the \"contents\" of communications within the meaning of the Wiretap Statute, as it does not include \"information concerning the substance, purport, or meaning\" of any communication. 18 U.S.C. s 2510(8). The Government is not requesting, and does not seek to obtain, the contents of any communications.2"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                122,
                92,
                857,
                245
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "title",
            "content": {
                "title_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "Certification and Request"
                    }
                ],
                "level": 2
            },
            "bbox": [
                387,
                258,
                606,
                275
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "8. I am familiar with the facts of this investigation from my review of relevant records and my discussions with the case agents involved. Based on those records and discussions, I hereby certify, pursuant to 18 U.S.C. 8 3123(a)(1), that the information likely to be obtained from the Requested Pen-Trap is relevant to the Investigating Agency's ongoing criminal investigation of the Target Subjects."
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                120,
                288,
                869,
                441
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "9. Accordingly, the Government requests that the Court enter an order authorizing the installation and use of the Requested Pen-Trap to collect the phone numbers and/or IP addresses and communications ports associated with any phone, text, or data communications to or from the Target Phone, along with the date, time, and duration (but not the contents) of the communication, for a period of 60 days."
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                120,
                454,
                861,
                606
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "10. The Government further requests, pursuant to 18 U.S.C. 88 3123(b)(2) and 3124(a)-(b), that the Order direct the Provider and any other person or entity providing wire or electronic communication service in the United States whose assistance may facilitate execution of this Order to furnish, upon service of the Order, any information, facilities, and technical assistance necessary to instal the Requested Pen-Trap unobtrusively and with minimum disruption of normal service. Any entity providing such assistance shall be reasonably compensated by the Investigating Agency, pursuant to 18 U.S.C. 8 3124(c), for reasonable expenses incurred in providing facilities and assistance in furtherance of this Order."
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                120,
                618,
                861,
                706
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "page_footnote",
            "content": {
                "page_footnote_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "2 The Government is also not seeking authorization to obtain post-cut-through dialed digits (\"PCTDD\"), or digits that are dialed after a telephone call from the Target Phone has been connected. Pursuant to the attached Order, if possible, the Provider will forward only pre-cutthrough-dialed digits to the Investigating Agency. However, if the Provider's technical capabilities require it to forward all dialed digits, including PCTDD, to the Investigating Agency, the Investigating Agency wil only decode and forward to the agents assigned to the investigation the numbers that are dialed before the call is cut through."
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                120,
                751,
                870,
                871
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "page_footer",
            "content": {
                "page_footer_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "2017.02.06"
                    }
                ]
